Hey, everybody getting the 

"You need to apply patch when licence screen appears" when applying the Mem patch.

the problem is, that you are not running it as an administrator; you first have to go to the crack file of your choice (x32 or x64) then right click on it, go to properties, then go to the compatibility tab, on the bottom the last case says "run program as an administrator" check that case, then click apply & then OK, then start the crack, the mem patch should be applied before you paste the authentification when you are in the licence screen...

hope this helps!
